Hartmarx Corp said Geoffrey Bloomresigned as president and chief executive officer of itsJaymar-Ruby Inc subsidiary to accept the position of presidentand chief operating officer of Wolverine World Wide Inc &lt;WWW>.    It said Elbert Hand, president and chief operating officerof Hartmarx, and president and chief executive officer of theHartmarx Men's Apparel Group, was named chief executive officerof Jaymar-Ruby Inc. Burton Ruby, son of the Jaymar-Rubyfounder, remains as chairman.           Reuter&#3;